<data>&lt;div class=b&gt;&lt;a href="/"&gt;Home&lt;/a&gt; » &lt;a href="/tipitaka/18It"&gt;18It Itivuttakapāḷi&lt;/a&gt; » &lt;a href="/tipitaka/18It/2"&gt;2 Dukanipāta&lt;/a&gt; » &lt;a href="/tipitaka/18It/2/2.2"&gt;2.2 Dutiyavagga&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="i"&gt;2.2.11 Āpāyikasutta&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=h&gt;Dukanipāta&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=h&gt;Dutiyavagga&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=h&gt;Āpāyikasutta&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="q" id="p_18It_306"&gt; &lt;div class="divNumber"&gt;48.&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="p"&gt;&lt;span class="pN"&gt;306&lt;/span&gt;Vuttañhetaṃ bhagavatā vuttamarahatāti me sutaṃ—  &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="q" id="p_18It_307"&gt; &lt;div class="p"&gt;&lt;span class="pN"&gt;307&lt;/span&gt;“Dveme, bhikkhave, āpāyikā nerayikā idamappahāya. Katame dve? Yo ca abrahmacārī brahmacāripaṭiñño, yo ca paripuṇṇaṃ parisuddhaṃ brahmacariyaṃ carantaṃ amūlakena abrahmacariyena anuddhaṃseti. Ime kho, bhikkhave, dve āpāyikā nerayikā idamappahāyā”ti. Etamatthaṃ bhagavā avoca. Tatthetaṃ iti vuccati—  &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="q" id="p_18It_308"&gt; &lt;div class="p"&gt; &lt;table class="singleColumn"&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="pN"&gt;308&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;“Abhūtavādī nirayaṃ upeti,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;Yo vāpi katvā na karomi cāha;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;Ubhopi te pecca samā bhavanti,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;Nihīnakammā manujā parattha.&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;/table&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="q" id="p_18It_309"&gt; &lt;div class="p"&gt; &lt;table class="singleColumn"&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="pN"&gt;309&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;Kāsāvakaṇṭhā bahavo,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;pāpadhammā asaññatā;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;Pāpā pāpehi kammehi,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;nirayaṃ te upapajjare.&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;/table&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="q" id="p_18It_310"&gt; &lt;div class="p"&gt; &lt;table class="singleColumn"&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="pN"&gt;310&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;Seyyo ayoguḷo bhutto,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;tatto aggisikhūpamo;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;Yañce bhuñjeyya dussīlo,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;raṭṭhapiṇḍamasaññato”ti.&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;/table&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="q" id="p_18It_311"&gt; &lt;div class="p"&gt;&lt;span class="pN"&gt;311&lt;/span&gt;Ayampi attho vutto bhagavatā, iti me sutanti. &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="CENTER" id="p_18It_312"&gt;&lt;span class="pN"&gt;312&lt;/span&gt;Ekādasamaṃ.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="tn"&gt;&lt;div class=plcb&gt;&lt;a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="prevP()" id="prevL" name="268422" title="Go to previous page"&gt;&amp;lt;&amp;lt; 2.2.10 Jāgariyasutta&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="upP()" id="upL" name="266886" title="Go to parent page"&gt;up&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="nextP()" id="nextL" name="268424" title="Go to next page"&gt;2.2.12 Diṭṭhigatasutta &amp;gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</data>
